# File: uc3-02
#
#   Uses 3 devices (expects file devices3-1.txt)
#
#   Shows the effect of two groups joining when a node B gets close to a node C
#author: borgez

clear
load devices3-1

# prologue

commit
wait 8

# step 1

move A (B)
creategroup A (B)
commit
wait

# step 2

move C (B)
creategroup C (B)
commit


